            <h3 class="highlight-text__header"> Pick up where you left off </h3> 
            <p class="highlight-text__subheader"> Microsoft 365 seamlessly tracks updates, task, and comments across all your files so you can pick up right where you left off </p> 
           </div> 
          </div> 
